      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) لَا يُعْجِبُكَ رَحْبُ الذِّرَاعَيْنِ بِالدَّمِ فَإِنَّ لَهُ عِنْدَ اللَّهِ قَاتِلًا لَا يَمُوتُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Abdul Rahman Bin Abu Najran, from Aasim Bin Humeyd, from Abu Ubeyda, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘Do not let the embrace of the two arms with the blood cause you to wonder, for it, in the Presence of Allah<sup>azwj</sup>, is a killer who does not die’."
        ]
      }
    }
